	   <tr><td colspan=2>With the new commands, you can set one button to function any spells that you want to chain cast.<br>Set up a button for stuns like this:<br>button name: STUN<br>/cast 1&nbsp;&nbsp;  (where the first spell on your screen is Color Flux)<br>/cast 2    (Color Shift)<br>/cast 3    (Color Skew)<br><br>When you hit the STUN button the first time, it will only cast the first spell.  The second time, it will cast the second if the first spell hasn't recovered yet.  You get the idea. <br><br>Embue<br>of Test<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
