	   <tr><td colspan=2>Giving your pet a weapon (even a rusty one) increases your pet's effectiveness in battle, as it will hit harder when it has a weapon. One negative, however, is that if you give them a weapon they can no longer hit mobs that are only hit by magic weapons (unless you give them a summoned dagger, etc.). And yes, the graphic will change :-)<br><br>Cubwynn<br>Ordo Ursi Prismatus<br>Lanys T'vyl<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
