	   <tr><td colspan=2>Just a quick note to all you Enchanters out there.&nbsp;&nbsp;If you are in a group with a Bard, make sure you talk to him about his AOE songs ;o)  Some Bards like to sing them when fighting Multiple mobs, since this really dishes out some damage.  But they will break your Mez.<br>Either He/She doesnt sing AOE, or You dont Mez.  Whatever you decide is fine, but the leader, or you and the Bard, need to decide on a course of action, otherwise, you will waste lots of Mana.<br>Besides that, and Enchanter Bard combo can do very well together as a duo or in a party.  His AOE debuffs and your Debuffs can make a a mob an easy target, and a weak hitter.<br>&nbsp;<br>Sapper Diesalot, At Deaths Door.&nbsp;&nbsp;"Chuck Berry cant twist this good!"</td></tr>
