	   <tr><td colspan=2>The problem I've had with being in groups is teaching other players to use /assist. Mez spells are useless when everyone keeps attacking their own targets and breaking the mez. Lay down the law from the start making them all hit one target, while you crowd control the rest, and you'll go far. And you'll also get a great rep as THE person to group with. High level groups know how good enchanters are, lower levels often wonder why they have such good reps. Make them understand!<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
