	   <tr><td colspan=2>I'd suggest putting more into INT originally myself. It's a lot easier to get larger CHA boosts earlier. For instance, you can add +28 CHA using 2 Elec Star Ruby Rings and 2 Gold Cat Eye Bracers.<br><br>Lots harder to add 28 INT using 2 rings and bracers.<br><br>However, do not neglect your CHA either. More mana isn't important if you can't get your mind spells to stick.<br>&nbsp;<br>Boueff Fhro'mahjj (33 MAG)<br>Arusab (51 ENC)<br>And a host of others<br>The CommuneXegony</td></tr>
