	   <tr><td colspan=2>Most enchanters will keep 2 sets of gear. One set for CHA, one set for INT. They will then change their gear to suit the type of MOBs, type of group, and the area inwhich they are fighting. Many of the better pieces of equipment for an enchanter come with bonuses to both stats so getting both INT and CHA to an acceptable level is not overly hard. Many Enchanters are now leaning towards the higher AC items especially at the higher levels. Basicly, if something works and you like it, stick with it.<br><br>Sobur<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
