	   <tr><td colspan=2> Personally, I have never really been satisfied by the standard charm on mob and let him fight to the death tactic. As soon as my pet is close to death(OR his opponent for that matter) I call him off, mem blur the target, and nuke it to death, thus insuring full exp instead of the usual 60% take.<br> Afterwards, I invis, and nuke my pet to death. 2 full exp kills for a mere bubble and a half of mana. Anything else I consider wasteful =P<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
